claim.claim-text:
4. A method for producing a color filter, the method comprising:
forming a photosensitive resin layer;
exposing the photosensitive resin layer;
developing the photosensitive resin layer; and
baking the photosensitive resin layer,
wherein the photosensitive resin layer comprises the colored photosensitive resin composition of claim 1.

7. A coating film of a colored photosensitive resin composition, wherein:
the colored photosensitive resin composition comprises an alkali-soluble binder, a monomer or an oligomer, a photopolymerization initiator or a photopolymerization initiator system, and a coloring agent;
the coloring agent comprises a pigment C.I.P.R.254 and a pigment C.I.P.R.177;
the content of the pigment C.I.P.R.254 in the coating film is 0.80 to 0.96 g/m2; and
the content of the pigment C.I.P.R.177 in the coating film is 0.20 to 0.24 g/m2.

9. A color filter comprising a red (R) photosensitive resin layer, a green (G) photosensitive resin layer, and a blue (B) photosensitive resin layer, wherein the red (R) photosensitive resin layer comprises the following coating film of a red (R) photosensitive resin layer, the green (G) photosensitive resin layer comprises the following coating film of a green (G) photosensitive resin layer, and the blue (B) photosensitive resin layer comprises the following coating film of a blue (B) photosensitive resin layer, where:
the coating film of a red (R) photosensitive resin layer is a coating film of a colored photosensitive resin composition, the composition comprising an alkali-soluble binder, a monomer or an oligomer, a photopolymerization initiator or a photopolymerization initiator system, and a coloring agent, in which:
the coloring agent comprises a pigment C.I.P.R.254 and a pigment C.I.P.R.177;
the content of the pigment C.I.P.R.254 in the coating film is 0.80 to 0.96 g/m2; and
the content of the pigment C.I.P.R.177 in the coating film is 0.20 to 0.24 g/m2;
the coating film of a green (G) photosensitive resin layer is a coating film of a colored photosensitive resin composition, the composition comprising an alkali-soluble binder, a monomer or an oligomer, a photopolymerization initiator or a photopolymerization initiator system, and a coloring agent, in which:
the coloring agent comprises a pigment C.I.P.G.36 and a pigment C.I.P.Y.150;
the content of the pigment C.I.P.G.36 in the coating film is 0.90 to 1.34 g/m2; and
the content of the pigment C.I.P.Y.150 in the coating film is 0.38 to 0.58 g/m2; and
the coating film of a blue (B) photosensitive resin layer is a coating film of a colored photosensitive resin composition, the composition comprising an alkali-soluble binder, a monomer or an oligomer, a photopolymerization initiator or a photopolymerization initiator system, and a coloring agent, in which:
the coloring agent comprises a pigment C.I.P.G.36 and a pigment C.I.P.Y.150;
the content of the pigment C.I.P.G.36 in the coating film is 0.90 to 1.34 g/m2; and
the content of the pigment C.I.P.Y.150 in the coating film is 0.38 to 0.58 g/m2.
